SUMMARY:The Basics of Brush Lettering
DESCRIPTION:Local Cary\, NC Artist Ann Erickson teaches the Basics of Brush Lettering on March 21\, 2026 from 10AM – 12PM at Trinity Park Church. You’ll enjoy the benefits of small-group teaching\, light refreshments\, and included supplies. This free event is appropriate for ages 10+ (please accompany your child). \nAnn will cover the basics of lines and strokes\, and by the end of the class\, participants will leave with their own creation. You’ll be able to take home your brush and a small gift.
URL:https://unitedarts.org/calendar/the-basics-of-brush-lettering/
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://unitedarts.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/510997307_23987574207575301_3084384965015410420_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
